column5: Absolutely fantastic!! You have a great talent.
Absolutely fantastic!! You are extremely talented.
Highly recommend Sinisterhood for your Bundy fix and pretty much every other episode they have released.

I could have written this. I currently feel exactly as you do. I'm so tired of disappointing everyone in my life. I truly believe they would be happier if I wasn't around. I'm a burden. I don't want my issues affecting their personal happiness a minute longer.
This is so good to hear. You should be proud of yourself. You made the choice to fight on and that is always admirable. Be well.
I care, but I can't say I'm surprised.

Your faking being happy comment hits home. It is sad but I have learned that feigning happiness is easier than watching people squirm to get out of a conversation in which I was honest and tried to talk about my depression. Unfortunately because I fake my happiness there is nobody out there that actually knows how bad I truly am.
I will do my part to make this answer a resounding NO! #votebluenomatterwho
